Azratek Package Archive Specification
=====================================
1. Archive Format

   File name extension: .apr

   Archived with tar and compressed with gzip.

2. Package Contents

   A "PACKAGE" file containing the package's information (package name, license, version,
   description, author, release date, and website).

   A "LICENSE" file containing the package's copyright and licensing information.

   A "DEPENDENCIES" file containing the package's dependencies.

   An "INSTALL" file containing the install script.

   An "UNINSTALL" file containing the uninstall script.

   A "docs" folder containing the package's documentation.

   A folder named after the package's name containing the installable files.
